Where you suppose to put the files to make the map and minimap work.
The Resource foldar suppose to go to:
C:>porgram Files>Steam>steam apps>>Counter Strike Source>Cstrike
The Materials foldar suppose to go to:
C:>porgram Files>Steam>steam apps>>Counter Strike Source>Cstrike
The Map Files foldar suppose to go to:
C:>porgram Files>Steam>steam apps>>Counter Strike Source>Cstrike>Maps
At the meterials and Resource foldars there is new 2 foldars just copy the foldars
and every thing will work.
